library(tidyverse)
library(tidytext)
library(gutenbergr)
library(wordcloud)
library (RColorBrewer)
data("stop_words")
dracula <- gutenberg_download(45839) %>% 
    mutate(linenumber=row_number()) %>% 
    unnest_tokens(word, text) %>% 
    anti_join(stop_words)
Joining with `by = join_by(word)`
dracula_counts <- dracula %>% count(word, sort=TRUE)
wordcloud(dracula_counts$word, dracula_counts$n, 
          min.freq=25, random.order=FALSE)

dracula_counts %>% with(wordcloud(word, n, 
                                   min.freq=25, random.order=FALSE))

dracula_counts %>% with(wordcloud(word, n, 
                                   min.freq=25, 
                                   random.order=FALSE,
                                   colors=brewer.pal(8, "Dark2")))

display.brewer.all()

sentiments <- get_sentiments("nrc")
dracula_sentiments <- dracula %>% 
                         inner_join(sentiments) %>% 
                         count(word, sentiment, sort=TRUE) %>% 
                         pivot_wider(names_from=sentiment, 
                                     values_from=n, 
                                     values_fill=0)
Joining with `by = join_by(word)`Warning: Detected an unexpected many-to-many relationship between `x` and `y`.
dracula_sentiments
dracula_sentiments %>% with(wordcloud(word, joy, 
                                       min.freq=10,
                                       random.color = FALSE,
                                       colors = brewer.pal(8, "PuOr")))

dracula_sentiments %>% with(wordcloud(word, fear, 
                                       min.freq=10,
                                       random.color = FALSE,
                                       colors = brewer.pal(12, "Paired")))
